        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/ct/v48/protocol/C132310-C71104>,
        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/ct/v48/protocol/C132310-C71473>,
        <http://id.gsk.com/dataset/cdisc/ct/v48/protocol/C132310-C93407>,
